nl.tudelft.simulation.dsol.formalisms.devs.ESDEVS

Interface OutputPortInterface<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of messages the input port accepts.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OutputPort

    public interface OutputPortInterface<T>
    OutputPortInterface class. Describes the contract for an output port of the Classic Parallel DEVS Atomic Model with Ports conform Zeigler et al (2000), section 4.2.2. and section 4.3 (pp. 84 ff).
